ZH: 我们必须保障公民的基本权利。
EN: We must ensure the basic rights of citizens.

ZH: 政府应该保障人民的安全。
EN: The government should guarantee the safety of the people.

ZH: 这份合同保障了消费者的权益。
EN: This contract ensures the rights of consumers.

ZH: 保障社会稳定是我们的责任。
EN: Ensuring social stability is our responsibility.

ZH: 这个政策将保障儿童的教育权。
EN: This policy will guarantee the right to education for children.

ZH: 保障员工的福利是企业的责任。
EN: It is the responsibility of the company to ensure the welfare of employees.

ZH: 我们要保障环境的可持续发展。
EN: We need to ensure the sustainable development of the environment.

ZH: 作为家长，你必须保障孩子的安全。
EN: As a parent, you must ensure the safety of your children.

ZH: 这个法律保障了人民的言论自由。
EN: This law guarantees freedom of speech for the people.

ZH: 保障消费者的合法权益是企业的义务。
EN: It is the duty of companies to safeguard the legitimate rights and interests of consumers.

ZH: 他们签订了一份协议保障双方的利益。
EN: They signed an agreement to safeguard the interests of both parties.

ZH: 拥有一份保险可以在紧急时保障你的财产。
EN: Having insurance can protect your property in emergencies.

ZH: 我们将采取措施来保障工人的安全。
EN: We will take measures to ensure the safety of workers.

ZH: 这个计划将保障每个人的基本权利。
EN: This plan will ensure the basic rights of everyone.

ZH: 我们要加强法律的执行，以保障社会秩序。
EN: We need to strengthen law enforcement to maintain social order.

ZH: 作为一个国家，我们要保障公民的人权。
EN: As a nation, we must protect the human rights of our citizens.

ZH: 为了保障合作的顺利进行，我们需要签订协议。
EN: To ensure smooth cooperation, we need to sign an agreement.

ZH: 他们将提供援助以保障灾民的生活。
EN: They will provide assistance to ensure the livelihood of disaster victims.

ZH: 政府投入资金以保障医疗服务的质量。
EN: The government invests funds to ensure the quality of medical services.

ZH: 这个组织的存在是为了保障弱势群体的权益。
EN: The existence of this organization is to safeguard the rights of vulnerable groups.
